Class Meal

java.lang.Object
bcu.cmp5332.bookingsystem.model.Meal
public class Meal extends Object
Represents a meal option available for selection on flights. Each meal has an ID, name, description, price, and a specific MealType.

    • Meal

      public Meal(int id, String name, String description, BigDecimal price, MealType type)
      Constructs a new Meal object.
      Parameters:
      id - The unique ID of the meal.
      name - The name of the meal (e.g., "Chicken Biryani").
      description - A brief description of the meal.
      price - The cost of the meal.
      type - The MealType (e.g., VEG, NON_VEG) of the meal.
